   stroke: currentColor, stroke-width: 2, round caps and joins) so they
   render consistently and pick up text colour.

   Args:
     - name:  one of the keys in the _ICONS dict below
     - title: optional accessible label. When omitted, the icon is
              marked aria-hidden (decorative use).
     - size:  CSS size; default is 1em (inherits font-size). Accepts
              any CSS length, or one of 'sm','md','lg','xl' for the
              preset sizes.

   Usage:
     {{ icon("mail") }}
     {{ icon("search", title="Search submissions") }}
     {{ icon("arrow-right", size="md") }}
#}

